`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Trigger_abuse
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Trigger abuse is when a player emotes, says, oocs, rptalks, notes, 
descriptions or conveys in any mode any type of output that would cause another
player's triggers  to go off. 

 An example of trigger abuse is if Player A has a trigger to eat a pie every
time the message "You are Hungry" appears on the screen, and Player B uses says
or emotes with the string "You are Hungry" to trigger off Player A's  eat pie
trigger.

